Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have the brain\Nthat controls the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are here to welcome us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they know why Yuito and us are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,within my range of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there are places I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, let me know if you spot anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, I'm counting on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The system Major General Fubuki gave us\Nis functioning normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,THE MOON'S SECRETS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please communicate with the history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Communicate? With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one else here except us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they want us to read the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't detect anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kyoka?\N-What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it showing Kyoka's image?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Name: Kyoka. Matched files: one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering a question regarding Kyoka Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She is one of the design children\Ncreated by Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Design? Created?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had heard rumors about design children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were created through\Na specific genetic combinations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a certain physical\Nappearance, strength, and brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I found some information as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka's explanation is pretty much on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's viable theoretically,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but it just can't work practically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kyoka was a design child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A brain power researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was created\Nwith Professor Hitoyo Pope's cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Pope is an expert\Nin the field of brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She is also the founder of Togetsu Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They share the same look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Professor Pope make Kyoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Professor Pope died about 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She is no longer of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She said 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was about the same time\NNew Himuka was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they have information about New Himuka\Nfrom that time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we dig around, we might find some dirt\Non the government too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was New Himuka like\Nwhen it was first founded?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering a question regarding\Nthe founding history of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka was founded 2020 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a country founded\Nby the people from the Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ark? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name of the immigrant group\Nthat moved to Earth from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They came from the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans originally lived on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But 300 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Earth's orbit underwent a drastic change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The catastrophe laid waste to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Human population was greatly reduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of human's continuity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they moved to the Moon\Nand built their new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to change Earth's environment\Nfrom the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After 1000 years of effort,\Nthe rehabilitation project came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth's condition was improved\Nto a certain degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon government sent\Nimmigrants back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were people from the Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only getting more confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans moved from Earth to the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they returned to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The immigrants from the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That means only a certain group of people\Nwere sent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there still people living on the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not have a clear answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The communication with the Moon government\Nhas been completely cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now. It must be the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the interference\Nfrom the Extinction Belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we have no way to know\Nthe condition on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Extinction Belt was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how did the immigrants get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Extinction Belt didn't exist back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Extinction Belt only appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,after the people came down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I know about history,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the Extinction Belt only appeared\Nafter the Spring of Extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spring of Extinction happened\Nduring the founding era.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Others and the Extinction belt\Nshowed up around the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Others came some time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,after the Extinction Belt appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't appear together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Others came from the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you make of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a little hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are the Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not possess the information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You require access to BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another system similar to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We got information Suoh and\NSeiran government don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up halfway through the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The information is simply unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We should only take it as a verbal legend\Npassed down in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's part\Nof the Togetsu Faith's scripture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If the immigrants founded New Himuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So our founding father, Yakumo Sumeragi,\Ncame from the Moon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as the hologram said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Yuito, but the whole\Nhuman population on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all descendants\Nof the immigrants from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Try asking something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us what you know\Nabout the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A question regarding the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunad Gate: A black hole that appeared\Nabove the Kunad Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gravitational pull is\Nabnormal and still growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It will consume the whole planet soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to Yuito Sumeragi's brain power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kunad Gate is still growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth's total destruction is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yuito part of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you need not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Place your faith in Togetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone will be granted salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon will protect all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! How is my power affecting the Kunad Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunad Gate is correcting trivial matters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and bringing the flawed universe\Nback to the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the very phenomenon\Nthat will bring the righteous future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The souls marching toward death
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will return to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, don't be concerned about the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Kunad Gate is indeed\Nconsuming its surrounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it grow to the point\Nwhere it consumes Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't believe those stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It might be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't be tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what shall we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned with the system named BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When we asked her about the Others,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,she said we'd require access to BABE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seek the knowledge of BABE?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is BABE?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the city computer that manages Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So it functions like Suoh's Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu has a management system too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead the way, please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi? Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We fell for Kyoka's trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer me! Kyoka! Shiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories we share
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will not perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two brains\Ncontrolling the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll reach our goal very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden, aren't you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you still lack the resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We are just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this to correct this flawed world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I need to borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is beckoning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, congratulations.\NYou're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The puppy is small like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at it barking. Don't you find it adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel this nostalgia, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious friend was murdered right before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The data is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't trigger her brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing her beloved animal\Ndoesn't bring enough stimuli to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hurting this poor child's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really for the sake of our future?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a Design Child created\Nfor this exact purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She is unlike the failure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of correcting this universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to secure the real future,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we need the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a need to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother. It was so warm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always trying to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I lost the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a need to correct the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is great as it is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what is this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome of your failed education\Nis beyond disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We only assigned you as her caretaker\Nso you'd have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you a great future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my caretaker that very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was created as a brain power user.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the Red Strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hurting this poor child's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,CONTACT LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop trying now, Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too noisy, I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you still sleep in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Panicking won't do us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We should rest while we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get some sleep too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I can sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane, we brought you new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it?\N-Verify it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The dashing prince is here to save his princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, please don't punch me in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You left the team\Nbefore we even entered Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in cahoot with Kyoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,why would I come here to rescue you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd regret coming to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain everything to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has become far worse after I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they got their hands on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and his team are here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito is here too? This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu is after my Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito probably has the same power as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I have no choice but to save them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kasane isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fun to meet the people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,from Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! Kagero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you two are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, where is Arashi and the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I can't contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew they'd be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where Yuito is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Yuito, this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,BABE will answer all of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Yuito, I'm sure you want to know\Nwhether the information was true or falsified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A conversation with BABE will clear your doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, verify it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too suspicious no matter how you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't let any outsider gain access\Nto the mainframe of Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too baffling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a religious group\Nneed this powerful computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we lost the psynet connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We must leave at once\Nas soon as we get the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Isn't some hologram going to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like the connection to SAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DESIGN CHILDREN
